WEBVTT

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:00.296
to find solutions

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:02.320
to anything that was needed.

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:06.200
She did all of this through isirika.

00:01:07.240 --> 00:01:09.656
Let me repeat that word for you again:

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:10.896
isirika.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:12.776
Now it's your turn. Say it with me.

00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:14.136
(Audience) Isirika.

00:01:14.160 --> 00:01:15.656
Musimbi Kanyoro: Thank you.

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:18.856
That word is in my language, Maragoli,

00:01:18.880 --> 00:01:20.656
spoken in western Kenya,

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:22.456
and now you speak my language.

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:23.816
(Laughter)

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:29.016
So, isirika is a pragmatic way of life

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:31.976
that embraces charity,